description: This was supposed to be a blow out. The Dragon was to whoop up on the newcomer. No one understood why Vendetta with one loss was ranked in the top ten. The Dragon has beaten every opponent this season by an average of 295pts. Not this time! I'll tell you this much: someone won by only 70 plus points. If you know US that is not many at all.
title: The Dragon (3-0) vs. Vendetta (0-1)
